name: CarBridge(Carplay iOS 11)
shortDescription: A plug-in that removes the system's Carplay restriction allows all APPs to shoot to the car. Of course, your car must support Carplay.Plug-in has been finished, you can use it free after installation. The chiefs removed a useless little video of about 2M. 100% full-featured unlimited, welcome!
author: Alex Stich
